        {
            "id": "urn:summary_document_slides:quartr.com:3888402:0",
            "title": "AOF: 12% revenue growth and 35% EBIT margin in H1 2026, led by strong cloud and AI momentum",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-Xl9a4Ubk body-nzzZVyQ3 content-nzzZVyQ3\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-uFduEtAF logosContainer-diQOvrPB\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>Revenue grew 12% year-over-year in H1 2026, driven by 26% growth in Cloud &amp; Subscriptions and a 35% EBIT margin, exceeding guidance. Strong recurring revenue and robust AI roadmap support continued double-digit growth, with 2026 revenue projected at €210m–€215m.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Original document: </span><a class=\"link-zw5jRdec\" href=\"https://www.tradingview.com/accounts/signin?next=https%3A%2F%2Fnews-mediator.tradingview.com%2Fdoc-screener%2Fv1%2Ffiles%2Furn%3Aslides%3Aquartr.com%3A3888402-c2c6e72cbbae330232f1780e466e0a9e\" target=\"_blank\">ATOSS Software SE [AOF] Slides Release — Jul. 24 2026</a></p><section class=\"variant-secondary-Gmpzg_mv disclaimer-PlF2Sa64\"><b class=\"heading-wrapper-Gmpzg_mv\"><span class=\"heading-Gmpzg_mv\">Disclaimer</span></b><div class=\"content-Gmpzg_mv link-with-underline-Gmpzg_mv\"><span>This is an AI-generated summary and may contain inaccuracies. Please verify any important information with the original source.</span></div></section></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/urn:summary_document_slides:quartr.com:3888402:0-aof-12-revenue-growth-and-35-ebit-margin-in-h1-2026-led-by-strong-cloud-and-ai-momentum/",
