        {
            "id": "urn:summary_document_report:quartr.com:3668906:0",
            "title": "LOOMIS: Record Q2 margins and growth, boosted by US and Latin America, with strong cash flow and acquisitions",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-Xl9a4Ubk body-nzzZVyQ3 content-nzzZVyQ3\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-uFduEtAF logosContainer-diQOvrPB\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>Q2 saw strong revenue and record margins, with robust growth in both USA and Europe/Latin America segments. Strategic acquisitions in Latin America and validated climate targets further strengthened the business, while cash flow and returns improved year-over-year.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Original document: </span><a class=\"link-zw5jRdec\" href=\"https://www.tradingview.com/accounts/signin?next=https%3A%2F%2Fnews-mediator.tradingview.com%2Fdoc-screener%2Fv1%2Ffiles%2Furn%3Areport%3Aquartr.com%3A3668906-053aeb4136989ff414a46643ecaea0cc\" target=\"_blank\">Loomis AB [LOOMIS] Interim report — Jul. 24 2026</a></p><section class=\"variant-secondary-Gmpzg_mv disclaimer-PlF2Sa64\"><b class=\"heading-wrapper-Gmpzg_mv\"><span class=\"heading-Gmpzg_mv\">Disclaimer</span></b><div class=\"content-Gmpzg_mv link-with-underline-Gmpzg_mv\"><span>This is an AI-generated summary and may contain inaccuracies. Please verify any important information with the original source.</span></div></section></span></div></div>",
